20:42.867 --> 20:44.617
<i> I just want back</i>

20:44.661 --> 20:46.827
<i> My sweet comic book gaijin.</i>

20:46.913 --> 20:49.121
[sobs]

20:49.207 --> 20:52.500
Once again, a critical lesson
is learned via hologram.

20:52.543 --> 20:55.253
I have been a fool.

20:55.380 --> 20:57.964
♪

21:17.151 --> 21:19.735
Best husband ever.

21:31.791 --> 21:33.207
Shh!
